00:08:00.644 --> 00:08:01.674
Ya, Bu.

00:08:07.984 --> 00:08:10.154
Aku hanya merasa sedikit pusing,

00:08:10.484 --> 00:08:14.054
Tapi Seong Jae menyeretku ke sini untuk melakukan CT scan.

00:08:14.954 --> 00:08:16.554
